snippet.title: Crystal Chasers League - First Trailer
snippet.description:
Crystal Chasers League is an Online Party Action game for PC. Use whimsical items, ground and aerial vehicles, jetpacks, and parachutes to reach victory. Players can play free-for-all or tag together in teams to win on modes like Crystal Captors and Triathlon Race. Play solo or with your friends via Split-Screen and/or Online.

Coming soon: https://PlayCrystalChasers.com 

Discord: https://discord.gg/xVVuyyv
